### 5. Neon-related error in `app/dashboard/page.tsx`

The dashboard shows a **"Database Setup Required"** alert in two cases:

1. **Empty data** (no invoices, clients, or payments) — lines 34–41  
2. **SQL error** containing `"does not exist"` — lines 236–252  

Both reference the same Neon script:

> *"The database tables haven't been created yet. Please run the SQL script `scripts/001_create_neon_schema.sql` from the Scripts section to set up your database."*

The Getting Started steps also tell users to run `001_create_neon_schema.sql`.

